{"word":"τοσόσδε","slug":"τοσόσδε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τοσόσδε</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:τόσος'><el>τόσος</el></a> in all senses, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>so strong, so able</i>, to do a thing, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>τοσόνδε</el>, epic <el>τοσσόνδε</el>, as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>so very, so much</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; of Time, <i>so long</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>τοσόνδ' ἔχεις τόλμης</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}